#: ../src/docs/guides/backup/mirroring_lsyncd.md:254
msgid ""
"`lsyncd` is a powerful tool for directory synchronization between computers. "
"As you've seen, it is not hard to install, and it is not complex to maintain "
"going forward. You can not ask for more than that."
msgstr ""

